<glossentry id="r-recognition-value">
    <glossterm>RRECOGNITIONVALUE</glossterm>
    <glossdef>
        <div><u>Definition, Placement, Relationships</u><p>This term, often used with <term
                    keyref="r-recogntions">RRECOGNITIONS</term>
                <menucascade>
                    <uicontrol><term keyref="writing">WRITING</term></uicontrol>
                    <uicontrol><term keyref="reception">RECEPTION</term></uicontrol>
                </menucascade>. It defines the numeric or non-monetary value of the recognition given
                for literary work. Generally encloses just a named sum, the amount of a literary
                prize, but its contents can be longer if a scholarship or travel grant is involved.
                This element has no mandatory or optional sub-elements or attributes.</p></div>
